---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Lone Ranger Roofing"
  description="Lone Ranger Roofing privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-12">Last updated: June 2025</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Introduction</h2>
          <p>Lone Ranger Roofing, LLC ("we," "us," or "our") operates lonerangerroofing.com. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or submit an inquiry.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, including your name, email address, phone number, physical address, and project details submitted through our website forms. We also collect usage data via cookies and analytics tools when you browse our site.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to respond to service inquiries, schedule estimates, communicate about your roofing project, and send appointment confirmations and project updates via phone, email, or text message.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">SMS / Text Messaging</h2>
          <p>When you opt in to SMS communications, you may receive text messages related to your estimate request, appointment scheduling, project updates, and follow-up. Message frequency is approximately 5–10 messages per month based on your project needs. We will never share your phone number or contact information with third parties for marketing purposes. Message and data rates may apply. You can opt out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">How We Store and Protect Your Information</h2>
          <p>Your information is stored securely and accessed only by authorized Lone Ranger Roofing personnel. We do not sell your personal information.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Third-Party Sharing</h2>
          <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. We may share information with service providers who assist in operating our business (e.g. CRM software, scheduling tools) under confidentiality agreements.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
          <p>Our website uses cookies and third-party analytics (Google Analytics, Meta Pixel) to understand how visitors interact with our site. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You may request to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@lonerangerroofing.com" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline font-semibold">info@lonerangerroofing.com</a> or <a href="tel:+12543001413" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline font-semibold">(254) 300-1413</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
          <address class="not-italic space-y-1 text-gray-600">
            <p class="font-bold text-brand-900">Lone Ranger Roofing, LLC</p>
            <p>715 E Downs Ave, Temple, TX 76501</p>
            <p><a href="tel:+12543001413" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">(254) 300-1413</a></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:lonerangerroofingtx@gmail.com" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">lonerangerroofingtx@gmail.com</a></p>
          </address>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
